&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a friendly and hardworking team member who is adaptable and who is a reflective practitioner committed to supporting the most disadvantaged young families in Lewisham. This is a demanding specialist role requiring high levels of professional skills and practice. As a Family Nurse you will be an effective communicator and listener with a compassionate nature and a commitment to delivering outstanding client care at all times&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kathleen Cruise, Family Nurse Supervisor, kathleen.cruise@nhs.net, 0203 049 2444&lt;/p&gt;
